<section class="main-section mdl-grid">
  <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-cell--8-col-tablet mdl-cell--4-col-phone main-section__cell">
    <div class="main-section_inner">
      <h1>About LeNe</h1>
      <p>
        Under the integration of all university resources LeNe aims to be an integrative teaching and learning program for refugees which can prepare them on the one hand for higher education or vocational training and on the other hand also provides meeting spaces and mutual exchange.
        <br><br>
        Here the mutual benefit of inclusion-oriented program for citizens of Friedrichshafen, ZU-students, faculty and staff of the University is a central concept component. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
